<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>sòng gěi nǐ yuǎn fāng qīn rén 迦南89</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 wǒ duō xiǎng jiàn dào nǐ, yō! yuǎn fāng de qīn rén.
 duō xiǎng kàn dào nǐ kě qīn de liǎn páng, tīng nǐ shuō huà de shēng yīn.
 wǒ de xīn wèi nǐ qí dǎo, zhù nǐ wàn shì rú yì,
 zhè shì wǒ de xīn yuàn, ràng fēng ér dài gěi nǐ.
 wǒ men yǒng yuǎn yǐ ài xiāng tōng, yǒng yuǎn yǐ ài xiāng xì
 bù lùn zài nán zài běi, zài dōng yě zài xī,
 tóng chàng yī shǒu gē, zhǔ ài wú bǐ,
 yīn tā shǐ wǒ men de xīn, nǎ zhēn chéng lián jiē zài yī qǐ.</lyrics>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<hymn_number>89</hymn_number>
</song>